Games-Tetris-Complete

Play Tetris on the console.

USAGE

perl -MGames::Tetris::Complete -e "play" [width height]

where optional arguments width and height are the board dimensions in 
pixels. They default to 12x20.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Games::Tetris::Complete

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Games-Tetris-Complete

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Games-Tetris-Complete

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Games-Tetris-Complete

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Games-Tetris-Complete/


